ProtoResult:
. "For an ergodic Markov chain, the components of the fixed 
   probability vector~{\bf w} are strictly positive. .2in {\bf 
   Proof.\ } We know that the values of $r_i$ are finite and so
   $w_i = 1/r_i$ cannot be 0."
